    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While it currently starts, the engine exhibits a rough idle and there are noticeable leaks that need to be addressed. The exterior has multiple dents and clear coat failure, while the interior shows heavy wear and several non-functional electronic components. This is a project car best suited for someone looking for a fixer-upper or a parts donor.",
