    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished acquisition for the discerning motorist, offering a superb synthesis of performance and sustained value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it features a refined interior paired with a robust, responsive powertrain. Every aspect of this automobile underscores a commitment to quality and mechanical integrity. We invite you to inspect this exceptional example of engineering, which stands as a testament to diligent ownership and professional care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
